{"tid":240440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東萬人抗建焚化爐　政府受壓下取消興建案","createTime":"2017-05-12T12:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T10:33:50.000Z","uid":105658,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6109b1fccd4874761a14496ad243a6bbc373364","tid":240440,"uid":105658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:10:07.000Z","msg":"[url<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20170511/37646546/[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Fappledaily%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170511%2F37646546%2F%5B%2Furl%5D&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=e76189f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20170511/37646546/[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n【大陸中心╱綜合外電報導】中國廣東省清遠市飛來峽鎮計劃興建垃圾焚化爐，遭當地居強烈反彈，上萬民眾7日起上街示威，民眾前天還發動罷工罷課抗議，當地警方一度施放胡椒噴霧與催淚彈鎮壓，並逮捕逾300人，情勢緊繃。當地政府不堪連日民意壓力，昨宣布取消這項興建案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台（RFA）報導，該垃圾焚化爐興建案，選址在黃竹坑水庫附近，但石梨村民認為政府未公開諮詢，且可能污染水源，本月初開始在村裡懸掛標語表達不滿，前晚數千民眾在市中心商業區示威，期間有人推翻警車，大批公安及鎮暴警員到場，施放胡椒噴霧與催淚彈驅離民眾，連日並有數百民眾被捕。 <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n政府低頭取消<br />\n<br />\n憤怒的村民前天集體罷工，包括計程車、小吃店、商店全部停擺，中學生也集體罷課，拿標語參與示威。在強大民意壓力下，市政府昨宣布取消焚化爐興建案，網友紛紛高呼：「清遠人民的勝利！」"},{"pid":"46f1a8a74a80eb03ee5a814fde131f1f4a7ac017","tid":240440,"uid":105658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"網上有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822950ee4f9fcb8c6200b6edd8b75e3fee2d45cc","tid":240440,"uid":82532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"講示威大陸人堅好多"},{"pid":"d97a5751b1ae5ddac91546b487d048536146a53d","tid":240440,"uid":105658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講示威大陸人堅好多</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e121fc7fadebd4e43743d051eb2549448d4c7aa8","tid":240440,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:16:06.000Z","msg":"睇錯廣東起萬人坑"},{"pid":"2471db7949f941e11f3721cf907129389a57eb84","tid":240440,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講示威大陸人堅好多</blockquote><br />\n佢哋一早知和理非無用"},{"pid":"1ec32c2a1ca777972f0d68c68e9286a6b8ff8414","tid":240440,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:18:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ec30528979f4f7d2ba3971f766377d3b6ae4f09","tid":240440,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港豬繼續唱今天我</blockquote><br />\n用愛與和平感化政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8492ba812829d1f08b8f8305f289bc746aa107bd","tid":240440,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:24:01.000Z","msg":"希望香港人都可以咁團結"},{"pid":"820a741a48facb369753ef8f71ece63dd7f77af1","tid":240440,"uid":24980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:24:56.000Z","msg":"香港人:好暴力啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286ac7ba60217fa043d66961d355480dc07011e6","tid":240440,"uid":17352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:26:00.000Z","msg":"高質市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70412133c92eb094ed8a1c28b99b9e3de48ffabb","tid":240440,"uid":5455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:28:45.000Z","msg":"口講取消，等風頭過左之後開始拉人<br />\n帶頭人比人拉哂之後，要起乜就起乜"},{"pid":"9e1dd86d3b97c1d750bcb1b58e891b9ff776bb8e","tid":240440,"uid":112502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:29:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[url<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20170511/37646546/[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2F