","tid":240440,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港豬繼續唱今天我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又有on9仔只係識踩香港人<br />\n<br />\n香港人夠有光復行動同魚革啦<br />\n你當時昏迷左定未出世??<br />\n<br />\n佔領旺角果陣, 有黑社會係旺角打學生, 全香港既人去旺角支援, 將D黑社會打到仆街, 你當時仲係老豆個春袋到??"},{"pid":"098dc03546967839e45fd9891ae2c53163981236","tid":240440,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T13:00:03.000Z","msg":"唔係震壓咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點可以讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337ad1cd432f5028ef7e2c0c3ccde2e210309608","tid":240440,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T13:02:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推翻警車仲推翻埋政府決定[yipes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係因為今次單野只係 興建垃圾焚化廠<br />\n對於政府來講, 影響不大, 所以政府先會屈服<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四川有個學生比人打死左, 跟住市民上街討回公道, 當地政府都唔屈服, 仲拉左死者家屬走<br />\n仲有兩個星期前, 廣西政府收地, D村民又係激烈反抗, 廣西出動十幾架裝甲車去鎮壓"},{"pid":"4e5f2b980e43e4f203c3e4723f11d49a6c0d5ed2","tid":240440,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T13:03:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係震壓咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點可以讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想睇鎮壓, 可以睇 幾個星期前既 四川瀘州和廣西南寧"},{"pid":"6b0b86860136e9fb0a1ba24f7642d8773c1a96b3","tid":240440,"uid":105658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3de9c5ebae987c60f6883f6141e2f5c79bca91c","tid":240440,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:07:44.000Z","msg":"竟然係政府輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 渣ga廣東省公安"},{"pid":"9d6223eee5c47b90cba985b470a293e16bfd1005","tid":240440,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:10:47.000Z","msg":"真．勇武"}]}